Beztam is an innovative app/expense tracking company based in Rabat, 
offering a user-friendly Android application that enables individuals to 
efficiently organize and track lent and borrowed money. The app provides a 
seamless and ergonomic experience, with upcoming AI capabilities that will 
score users based on their debt repayment history, promoting timely settlements. 
Beztam offers a free version with optional ads, as well as a paid tier that grants 
full access to its AI features. For more, contact MyBeztam@gmail.com